ossible for quantum protocols. In the final result in the theme\nof message compression, we provide an upper bound on the problem of Exact\nRemote State Preparation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Jul 2008 15:05:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-07-09"}
